''' Bust gez dam ''' (from {{lang-ar|''' سَّد بست گز '''}}, in {{lang-fa| سد بَستِ گِز}}) also known as ''' Bast gez dam ''', is a dam in [[Kukherd]] city, southwestern [[Kukherd District]], [[Hormozgan Province]], Iran.
==Geology== [[Bust gez Valley]] basin is located in the southern part of [[Zeer Mountain]] and southern Dasak Mountain is a beg Mount from [[Kukherd District]] ({{lang-fa|بخش كوخرد}}) in the [[city]] of Kukherd in [[Bastak County]] (شهرستان بستک) Hormozgan Province. Is a modern dam which was built in 2005 in southern mountain.
